data.name: txtQuery.Text
data.value:
select A.InventoryCode,A.VariantId1,A.VariantId2,A.VariantType1,A.VariantType2,A.Renk,A.Beden, A.VariantTypeId1,A.VariantTypeId2, A.Fiyatii, A.KDVTotal, A.Indirimlii, A.IsPriceDiscount,A.InventoryVID,sum(A.ActualStock) ActualStock, A.Barcode,A.WarehouseId,W.WarehouseCode from ( select I.InventoryCode, v1.ItemName as Renk, v2.ItemName as Beden, isnull((IT.ActualStock), 0) ActualStock, (select top 1 ITY.TypeName from Erp_VariantType ITY with(nolock) where ITY.RecId=IV.Variant1TypeId) as VariantType1, (select top 1 ITY.TypeName from Erp_VariantType ITY with(nolock) where ITY.RecId=IV.Variant2TypeId) as VariantType2, (select top 1 ITY.RecId from Erp_VariantType ITY with(nolock) where ITY.RecId=IV.Variant1TypeId) as VariantTypeId1, (select top 1 ITY.RecId from Erp_VariantType ITY with(nolock) where ITY.RecId=IV.Variant2TypeId) as VariantTypeId2, (select IB.Barcode from Erp_InventoryBarcode IB with(nolock) where IV.RecId=IB.InventoryVariantId and I.RecId=IB.InventoryId) as Barcode, Fiyat.Fiyat as Fiyatii, IndirimliFiyat.Fiyat as Indirimlii, T.TaxCode [KDVTotal],
IT.WarehouseId,IV.RecId as 'InventoryVID',v1.RecId as VariantId1,v2.RecId as VariantId2, (select top 1 IsPriceDiscount from Erp_InventoryPriceList ipl where ipl.InventoryId = I.RecId and ipl.InventoryVariantId = IV.RecId ) IsPriceDiscount
from Erp_Inventory I left join Erp_InventoryVariant IV on (IV.InventoryId = I.RecId) left join Erp_VariantItem v1 with(nolock) on v1.RecId = IV.Variant1Id left join Erp_VariantItem v2 with(nolock) on v2.RecId = IV.Variant2Id left join Erp_InventoryTotal IT with(nolock) on IT.InventoryId = I.RecId and IT.InventoryVariantId = IV.RecId and IT.TotalDate is not null and IT.InventoryVariantId is not null left join Erp_Tax T with(nolock) on T.RecId=I.VatId
outer apply ( Select IPL.Price [Fiyat] from Erp_InventoryPriceList IPL with(nolock) where IPL.PriceType=2 and PriceCode='3' and IPL.InventoryId=I.RecId )Fiyat
outer apply ( Select IPL.Price [Fiyat] from Erp_InventoryPriceList IPL with(nolock) where IPL.PriceType=2 and PriceCode='2' and IPL.InventoryId=I.RecId )IndirimliFiyat
where IV.InUse = 1 and I.IsPublishWeb=1) A left join Erp_Warehouse W on W.RecId=A.WarehouseId
where A.WarehouseId=(select top 1 RecId from Erp_Warehouse with(nolock) where WarehouseCode='01') group by A.Renk,A.Beden,A.VariantType1,A.VariantType2,A.IsPriceDiscount,A.WarehouseId,A.VariantId1,A.VariantId2,A.VariantTypeId1,A.VariantTypeId2,A.InventoryVID,A.Barcode,A.InventoryCode,W.WarehouseCode, A.Fiyatii,A.Indirimlii,A.KDVTotal
order by A.InventoryCode
